description: Demolition of existing building and erection of a building comprising commercial floorspace (Class E), Purpose built student accommodation bedrooms and amenity space (sui generis), refuse and bike stores, internal and external plant, and external landscaping.For information: - proposed building is part 19 storeys with additional rooftop lift/overrun/enclosure plus basement (62.8m AOD, 59.9m above ground), part 18 storeys (58.3m AOD, 55.4m above ground) and part 3 storeys (14.7m AOD, 11.8m above ground).  The development as a whole comprises:- 243 student bedrooms;- 1,504sqm GIA of flexible commercial, business, service floorspace (Class E)
site_name: Coburg House63-67 Newington CausewayLondonSouthwarkSE1 6LS
